ocker buildx use backflow-builder\n\ndocker buildx build \\\n    --platform linux/amd64,linux/arm64 \\\n    -t \"${ECR_URI}:latest\" \\\n    --push \\\n    docker/\n\necho \"==> Pushed to ${ECR_URI}:latest\"\n","numLines":25,"startLine":1,"totalLines":25}}}
